Starting this Black Friday, Cell C is offering a prepaid data SIM loaded with 50GB of data for R500 – R10 per Gigabyte. “This is the perfect option for those going on holiday this Festive season. Consumers can stay connected wherever they are. Simply pop the SIM in a router to connect your holiday spot or slide it into a tablet and keep your kids entertained all the way to your holiday destination,” said Junaid Munshi, Cell C chief commercial officer. The data will be valid for six months from the date of activation and can be used at any time of the day. There are no restrictions on the data, Cell C said, adding that the offer is limited to three per customer. The offer opens on Friday, 23 November, at Cell C stores and runs until 25 November. Read: Cell C completes roaming agreement with MTN